name: MY LINE #86 -- derivative art piece
description:
Here is a derivative piece based on my Line #86

"The Line of Fire"

This piece is dedicated to a great artist and 
friend in the #NFT space @mynameistru3

I captured a little bit of his pop art collage style on this one.
Give him a follow and check out his CHEEPCARDZ and other 1/1 peices.

You also will note an appearance of my very own #wackywaffles in here, you can check out that fun collection at wackywaffles.tez on OBJKT and HEN.

Find out about Dr. Soundwaves amazing LINES project and get on board.
